    "The consumer expectation test thus connects product liability to the information available to consumers.",
    "As mentioned earlier, the courts are not bound by industry safety standards when determining the legitimate safety expectations of the public.",
    "In the context of AI, regulatory standards can only provide guidance but no guarantee for the standard in product liability.",
    "73 It would be useful to rely more on regulation and certification standards to guide the concept of defect in the context of AI.",
    "This would provide more legal certainty than the consumer expectation or risk-utility tests."
